  rhythmbox-0.9.4.1.ebuild:
  Back to ~sparc wrt #135411

*rhythmbox-0.9.4.1 (02 Jun 2006)

  02 Jun 2006; Joe McCann <joem@gentoo.org>
  files/rhythmbox-0.9.4_p1-libnotify.patch, -rhythmbox-0.9.2.ebuild,
  -rhythmbox-0.9.3.1.ebuild, -rhythmbox-0.9.3.1_p1.ebuild,
  +rhythmbox-0.9.4.1.ebuild:
  New bugfix release, update python use deps, only support gstreamer-0.10 as
  it is prefered by upstream and gst-0.8 is depreciated by gstreamer upstream

  17 May 2006; Daniel Gryniewicz <dang@gentoo.org>
  +files/rhythmbox-0.9.4_p1-libnotify.patch, rhythmbox-0.9.4_p1.ebuild:
  Fix bug #131705

  27 Apr 2006; Marien Zwart <marienz@gentoo.org>
  files/digest-rhythmbox-0.8.8-r1, files/digest-rhythmbox-0.9.2,
  files/digest-rhythmbox-0.9.3.1, files/digest-rhythmbox-0.9.3.1_p1,
  Manifest:
  Fixing SHA256 digest, pass four

